1
00:00:23,920 --> 00:00:24,800
What happened?

2
00:00:25,680 --> 00:00:27,280
I ran into two thugs just now.

3
00:00:27,560 --> 00:00:28,720
Qingzhou saved me

4
00:00:29,080 --> 00:00:30,480
and got me out of trouble.

5
00:00:32,040 --> 00:00:32,800
Where are they?

6
00:00:32,800 --> 00:00:33,560
She was hurt,

7
00:00:33,880 --> 00:00:35,480
so I didn't chase after them.

8
00:01:30,760 --> 00:01:31,820
What are you doing?

9
00:01:31,880 --> 00:01:32,880
Why so resistant?

10
00:01:33,560 --> 00:01:35,200
Didn't you say we should bond?

11
00:01:35,200 --> 00:01:36,460
I can't even touch you?

12
00:01:41,280 --> 00:01:42,440
To me,

13
00:01:42,440 --> 00:01:42,840
you're just

14
00:01:42,840 --> 00:01:44,570
a stranger I've met a few times.

15
00:01:49,080 --> 00:01:51,080
But when my brother held you just now,

16
00:01:51,080 --> 00:01:52,340
you were quiet enough.

17
00:01:54,039 --> 00:01:57,170
You care a lot about my relationship with Song Qingzhou.

18
00:02:00,760 --> 00:02:01,690
Yao Shengsheng.

19
00:02:01,960 --> 00:02:02,840
I just hope

20
00:02:02,840 --> 00:02:04,320
you remember your place.

21
00:02:05,560 --> 00:02:06,290
Understand?

22
00:02:09,560 --> 00:02:10,960
Don't think I don't know.

23
00:02:11,039 --> 00:02:12,000
You're marrying me

24
00:02:12,000 --> 00:02:13,730
just for the Yao family assets.

25
00:02:14,360 --> 00:02:15,280
But as for me,

26
00:02:15,440 --> 00:02:16,920
I only want to marry someone I love.

27
00:02:16,920 --> 00:02:18,579
I hope the one you want to marry

28
00:02:18,640 --> 00:02:19,900
is me, Yao Shengsheng,

29
00:02:20,200 --> 00:02:22,130
not the daughter of the Yao family.

30
00:02:25,400 --> 00:02:26,640
Didn't you promise

31
00:02:27,120 --> 00:02:29,050
you'd make me willing to marry you?

32
00:02:29,400 --> 00:02:30,329
Commander Song.

33
00:02:41,680 --> 00:02:42,840
Interesting.

34
00:02:57,920 --> 00:02:58,850
Why are you here?

35
00:03:12,480 --> 00:03:14,120
This medicine is very effective.

36
00:03:14,120 --> 00:03:15,720
You'll recover in a few days.

37
00:03:31,960 --> 00:03:32,690
Bear with it.

38
00:03:57,960 --> 00:03:58,560
Done.

39
00:03:59,240 --> 00:03:59,880
Thank you.

40
00:04:24,040 --> 00:04:24,970
Why are you here?

41
00:04:27,920 --> 00:04:28,650
Give it to me.

42
00:04:36,320 --> 00:04:37,600
Have you grown taller?

43
00:04:37,600 --> 00:04:39,060
You've gotten bolder too.

44
00:04:39,880 --> 00:04:41,840
Brother, why should I give it to you?

45
00:04:41,840 --> 00:04:43,760
You know this belongs to her, right?

46
00:04:43,760 --> 00:04:44,440
I know.

47
00:04:44,960 --> 00:04:46,360
She is just your fiancée.

48
00:04:46,680 --> 00:04:48,740
A woman you haven't even married yet.

49
00:04:51,320 --> 00:04:52,250
What did you say?

50
00:04:53,159 --> 00:04:54,159
Am I wrong?

51
00:04:55,560 --> 00:04:56,200
Can a piece of paper

52
00:04:56,200 --> 00:04:57,680
restrict a person's freedom?

53
00:04:57,680 --> 00:04:58,440
Can a piece of paper

54
00:04:58,440 --> 00:04:59,800
hold someone's feelings hostage?

55
00:04:59,800 --> 00:05:00,800
I am your brother.

56
00:05:00,800 --> 00:05:01,640
Since when is it your turn

57
00:05:01,640 --> 00:05:03,120
to lecture me?

58
00:05:03,120 --> 00:05:04,320
What about Zhu Luoli?

59
00:05:04,400 --> 00:05:06,680
The last person you bound with a piece of paper,

60
00:05:06,680 --> 00:05:07,520
do you still love her?

61
00:05:07,520 --> 00:05:07,920
Do you believe

62
00:05:07,920 --> 00:05:09,720
I'll kick you out of the military academy tomorrow?

63
00:05:09,720 --> 00:05:10,520
I believe you.

64
00:05:10,880 --> 00:05:12,200
With just one word from you,

65
00:05:12,200 --> 00:05:14,320
let alone kicking me out of the academy,

66
00:05:14,320 --> 00:05:16,080
even if you kick me out of the family,

67
00:05:16,080 --> 00:05:16,680
is there anyone

68
00:05:16,680 --> 00:05:18,010
who would dare to say no?

69
00:05:21,560 --> 00:05:22,420
Song Qingzhou.

70
00:05:24,160 --> 00:05:25,820
Is this what you really think?

71
00:05:30,920 --> 00:05:31,400
Don't.

72
00:05:34,720 --> 00:05:36,360
You're not a child anymore.

73
00:05:36,880 --> 00:05:38,280
Stop throwing tantrums.

74
00:05:38,680 --> 00:05:39,320
Don't think I don't know

75
00:05:39,320 --> 00:05:40,840
what you're doing right now.

76
00:05:40,840 --> 00:05:42,200
Stop it right now.

77
00:05:42,400 --> 00:05:42,800
Yes.

78
00:05:43,159 --> 00:05:44,200
I'm not a child.

79
00:05:44,640 --> 00:05:45,280
So don't try to use

80
00:05:45,280 --> 00:05:47,120
your authority as an older brother

81
00:05:47,120 --> 00:05:47,980
to pressure me.

82
00:05:50,280 --> 00:05:51,720
Did you drop your bracelet?

83
00:05:51,720 --> 00:05:52,440
I'm sorry,

84
00:05:52,680 --> 00:05:53,400
I broke it.

85
00:05:55,920 --> 00:05:56,920
My brother gave me this.

86
00:05:56,920 --> 00:05:58,360
It's a very important gift.

87
00:05:58,360 --> 00:06:00,620
How can I explain it to him if it's broken?

88
00:06:01,560 --> 00:06:02,220
Count them.

89
00:06:02,520 --> 00:06:04,050
See if anything is missing.

90
00:06:07,600 --> 00:06:09,440
I'll find someone to fix it for you.

91
00:06:09,440 --> 00:06:11,100
And I'll return it to you then.

92
00:06:31,360 --> 00:06:33,240
Looks like my plan worked.

93
00:06:34,440 --> 00:06:36,040
I want to see just how long

94
00:06:36,040 --> 00:06:37,159
you two brothers

95
00:06:37,159 --> 00:06:39,880
can keep up this superficial peace.

96
00:06:44,320 --> 00:06:44,850
Marshal.

97
00:06:46,600 --> 00:06:48,530
We have a lead on the secret recipe.

98
00:06:50,280 --> 00:06:51,240
Where is the secret recipe?

99
00:06:51,240 --> 00:06:51,960
I've been having Zhang Qi

100
00:06:51,960 --> 00:06:53,400
secretly search the Zhu residence.

101
00:06:53,400 --> 00:06:54,760
But he had the nerve

102
00:06:54,760 --> 00:06:57,000
to steal the secret recipe.

103
00:06:57,000 --> 00:06:57,480
What good are you?

104
00:06:57,480 --> 00:06:59,480
You can't even control your own men.

105
00:07:01,200 --> 00:07:03,360
So Song Huainan's goal...

106
00:07:03,360 --> 00:07:05,690
They want the Zhu family's secret recipe.

107
00:07:07,000 --> 00:07:08,080
Go find him.

108
00:07:08,080 --> 00:07:09,680
The situation is tricky now.

109
00:07:09,720 --> 00:07:12,980
I heard the Young Marshal is going to find Zhang Qi himself.

110
00:07:13,000 --> 00:07:14,480
How did Qingzhou get involved?

111
00:07:14,480 --> 00:07:17,610
He has always been in charge of tracking down deserters.

112
00:07:19,080 --> 00:07:20,560
Find a way to stop Qingzhou.

113
00:07:20,560 --> 00:07:21,720
He must not know about the secret recipe

114
00:07:21,720 --> 00:07:23,000
or the Zhu family affairs.

115
00:07:23,000 --> 00:07:23,730
Understood.

116
00:07:23,880 --> 00:07:24,740
Could it be that

117
00:07:24,840 --> 00:07:27,520
Song Qingzhou knows nothing about any of this?

118
00:07:39,280 --> 00:07:39,920
Song Qingzhou,

119
00:07:39,920 --> 00:07:41,480
why do you keep hounding me?

120
00:07:41,480 --> 00:07:43,400
I despise deserters more than anything.

121
00:07:43,400 --> 00:07:44,720
Today, I will personally

122
00:07:44,720 --> 00:07:45,840
take you back.

123
00:07:51,280 --> 00:07:53,340
Then I must commit insubordination.

124
00:07:58,800 --> 00:07:59,400
Watch out!

125
00:08:06,120 --> 00:08:07,050
Why are you here?

126
00:08:07,160 --> 00:08:07,960
If I hadn't followed you,

127
00:08:07,960 --> 00:08:08,760
you'd be dead.

128
00:08:09,960 --> 00:08:11,920
You deserted before the battle even started.

129
00:08:11,920 --> 00:08:13,780
You'd better go back and confess.

130
00:08:14,240 --> 00:08:15,100
Young Marshal,

131
00:08:15,160 --> 00:08:16,320
it's not that I won't go back.

132
00:08:16,320 --> 00:08:17,240
But if I do,

133
00:08:17,400 --> 00:08:18,800
I'll die without a grave.

134
00:08:18,800 --> 00:08:19,360
Why?

135
00:08:19,880 --> 00:08:20,720
Because...

136
00:08:29,080 --> 00:08:29,810
Are you okay?

137
00:08:34,080 --> 00:08:34,940
Song Qingzhou.

138
00:08:38,440 --> 00:08:39,240
Are you okay?
